<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 06:12:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国希望阻止伊朗对以色列的重大袭击，而真主党仍然是未知数</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/fearing-catastrophic-war-biden-warns-iran-against-attack-pushes-pm-to-make-deal/00000191-2de7-da6f-af99-2de71f1d0000</link><description>美国和以色列官员相信，真主党对杀害一名高级官员的报复将集中在军事地点，但他们不能肯定地说，真主党会多么谨慎地避免伤害平民</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 03:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/fearing-catastrophic-war-biden-warns-iran-against-attack-pushes-pm-to-make-deal/00000191-2de7-da6f-af99-2de71f1d0000</guid></item><item><title>辛瓦尔的晋升可能不会改变哈马斯在与以色列人质谈判中的立场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/sinwars-promotion-likely-wont-change-in-hamas-stance-in-hostage-talks-with-israel/00000191-2e07-d1b4-a399-7ea78a9c0000</link><description>任命叶海亚·辛瓦尔担任哈马斯政治局高层的决定是实际需要，对以色列来说可能没有媒体所描述的那么重要。然而，对于哈马斯来说，辛瓦尔是一位与哈尼亚截然不同的领导人，他可能会面临挑战</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 03:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/sinwars-promotion-likely-wont-change-in-hamas-stance-in-hostage-talks-with-israel/00000191-2e07-d1b4-a399-7ea78a9c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡很想解雇他的国防部长，但不相信其他选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-would-love-to-boot-his-defense-minister-but-doesnt-trust-the-alternative/00000191-2e3c-da6f-af99-2e7e6c7d0000</link><description>由于大多数联盟认为全面的地区战争是一个有价值的目标，总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡似乎将坚持国防部长约阿夫·加兰特的政策——至少目前如此</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 03:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-would-love-to-boot-his-defense-minister-but-doesnt-trust-the-alternative/00000191-2e3c-da6f-af99-2e7e6c7d0000</guid></item><item><title>报道：真主党可能先于伊朗攻击以色列；德黑兰可能“重新考虑”报复范围</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article-live/u-s-says-cease-fire-deal-closer-than-ever-cnn-hezbollah-could-attack-israel-without-iran/00000191-2fb9-d759-a795-bfff7dd90000</link><description>伊朗外长表示，将在“正确的时间以适当的方式”作出回应 ■ 加拿大批准将外交官的子女和监护人临时迁出以色列 ■ 以色列国防军称，策划约旦河西岸恐怖袭击的哈马斯高级成员在加沙被杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 02:13:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article-live/u-s-says-cease-fire-deal-closer-than-ever-cnn-hezbollah-could-attack-israel-without-iran/00000191-2fb9-d759-a795-bfff7dd90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列右翼声称受到迫害。这是无耻的谎言</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-right-wing-claims-to-be-persecuted-its-a-shameless-lie/00000191-2d8c-d200-a9f9-adcd6e7a0000</link><description>对某些人不平等地运用法律，同时又未能追究其他人的责任的做法在以色列可以追溯到很久以前，但不是针对右翼</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 20:18:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-right-wing-claims-to-be-persecuted-its-a-shameless-lie/00000191-2d8c-d200-a9f9-adcd6e7a0000</guid></item><item><title>美国：“比以往任何时候都更接近”加沙停火；西方外交官称谈判仍陷入僵局</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-closer-than-ever-to-cease-fire-in-gaza-western-diplomats-say-talks-still-stuck/00000191-2e0e-d4e9-a7b7-2fce7d1c0000</link><description>国家安全委员会发言人约翰·柯比声称，一项协议已经摆在桌面上，但参与以色列与哈马斯谈判的西方外交官否认了解谈判取得突破</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 19:45:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-closer-than-ever-to-cease-fire-in-gaza-western-diplomats-say-talks-still-stuck/00000191-2e0e-d4e9-a7b7-2fce7d1c0000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列最后的常态堡垒中，紧张地等待伊朗的报复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-07/ty-article/.highlight/in-israels-last-bastions-of-normalcy-waiting-nervously-for-irans-revenge/00000191-2d53-d1b4-a399-7df7cc470000</link><description>这种等待的游戏是攻击的一部分——哈桑·纳斯鲁拉甚至说过同样的话——也许伊朗和真主党希望悬念确实会杀死我们</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 18:48:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-07/ty-article/.highlight/in-israels-last-bastions-of-normalcy-waiting-nervously-for-irans-revenge/00000191-2d53-d1b4-a399-7df7cc470000</guid></item><item><title>美国犹太人在观看以色列的犹太至上主义暴徒时并没有感到更安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/u-s-jews-dont-feel-safer-when-they-watch-israels-jewish-supremacist-mobs/00000191-2806-dbbc-ab95-3957c76c0000</link><description>如果以色列想继续成为所有犹太人的家园，就不能放松对保护所有人的民主自由价值观的警惕</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 17:33:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/u-s-jews-dont-feel-safer-when-they-watch-israels-jewish-supremacist-mobs/00000191-2806-dbbc-ab95-3957c76c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 306 天：世卫组织将向加沙运送超过 100 万支脊髓灰质炎疫苗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-306-who-to-send-gaza-over-one-million-polio-vaccines/00000191-2dbe-da6f-af99-2dfe6cee0001</link><description>白宫表示，“我们距离达成我们所认为的最接近”的人质释放/停火协议 ■ 据报道，联黎部队官员的家属已从黎巴嫩撤离 ■ 土耳其正式要求加入南非对国际法院的诉讼，指控以色列在叙利亚实施种族灭绝加沙 ■ 德国和法国拒绝接受以色列财政部长的言论，即让 200 万加沙人挨饿是“正确且道德的” ■ 战争已过去 306 天，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 17:00:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-306-who-to-send-gaza-over-one-million-polio-vaccines/00000191-2dbe-da6f-af99-2dfe6cee0001</guid></item><item><title>以色列新闻频道忠实内塔尼亚胡首席执行官因记者强烈反对而被撤换</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/newly-appointed-ceo-of-israeli-new-channel-to-be-replaced-after-journalists-backlash/00000191-2d8e-d1b4-a399-7dae6d8f0000</link><description>尤利娅·沙马洛夫-贝尔科维奇被任命为以色列第 13 频道的负责人是有争议的，因为她公开支持内塔尼亚胡的立场，但在她被记录说“电视台里有很多坏记者”后，员工的反抗导致该频道宣布她将被任命为以色列第 13 频道的负责人。被取代</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 16:47:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/newly-appointed-ceo-of-israeli-new-channel-to-be-replaced-after-journalists-backlash/00000191-2d8e-d1b4-a399-7dae6d8f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长与 Black Cube 就监视亲巴勒斯坦的美国学生团体举行会谈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-held-talks-with-black-cube-about-spying-on-pro-palestinian-u-s-students/00000191-2d2b-d927-a5b5-ff7f03690000</link><description>侨民事务部长 Amichai Chikli 于 6 月与 Black Cube 会面，讨论可能对巴勒斯坦学生正义组织执行间谍任务，该组织在美国校园领导反以色列抗议活动。该部称 Black Cube 向其提出了这个想法，但消息人士称事实恰恰相反</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:19:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-held-talks-with-black-cube-about-spying-on-pro-palestinian-u-s-students/00000191-2d2b-d927-a5b5-ff7f03690000</guid></item><item><title>法国和德国猛烈抨击以色列斯莫特里奇关于饿死加沙人的言论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/france-germany-slam-israels-smotrich-for-comments-on-starving-gazans-to-death/00000191-2d2f-d4ad-a7ff-fd3fc82b0000</link><description>法国和德国外交部谴责这位右翼部长，几天前他暗示国际压力是以色列不让加沙人饿死的唯一原因</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:15:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/france-germany-slam-israels-smotrich-for-comments-on-starving-gazans-to-death/00000191-2d2f-d4ad-a7ff-fd3fc82b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列周围的火圈：伊朗、真主党和胡塞武装的军火库</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/the-ring-of-fire-around-israel-a-look-at-the-arsenals-of-iran-hezbollah-and-the-houthis/00000191-2ce3-d927-a5b5-ffff7b5c0000</link><description>从远程巡航导弹到携带炸弹的无人机，以色列的敌人可能会对其防空系统进行前所未有的考验</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 14:29:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/the-ring-of-fire-around-israel-a-look-at-the-arsenals-of-iran-hezbollah-and-the-houthis/00000191-2ce3-d927-a5b5-ffff7b5c0000</guid></item><item><title>超过 110 名记者在加沙被杀。以色列同行保持沉默</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/over-110-journalists-have-been-killed-in-gaza-their-israeli-colleagues-keep-silent/00000191-2c36-daed-a3ff-af3f92620000</link><description>太多的以色列记者将某种程度的罪责归咎于他们在加沙的同行——甚至认为他们是应该死的努赫巴部队成员</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 12:33:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/over-110-journalists-have-been-killed-in-gaza-their-israeli-colleagues-keep-silent/00000191-2c36-daed-a3ff-af3f92620000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩担心伊朗和真主党的反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/lebanon-waits-in-fear-for-iran-and-hezbollahs-response/00000191-2c88-d1b4-a399-7cae8b7f0000</link><description>边境地区的人们正在储存食物和水，等待以色列对贝鲁特的猛烈袭击。 “哈尼亚被暗杀后，我们意识到我们不能留在黎巴嫩。我们告诉孩子们，情况不安全，我们必须离开。”一位正在回国的法国妇女说道。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 12:19:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/lebanon-waits-in-fear-for-iran-and-hezbollahs-response/00000191-2c88-d1b4-a399-7cae8b7f0000</guid></item><item><title>“新犹太人”的象征如何最终被装进盒子里——并陷入法律纠纷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-the-symbol-of-the-new-jew-ended-up-in-a-box-and-in-a-legal-dispute/00000191-2bd0-d2a9-a5dd-3fd966b60000</link><description>以色列博物馆展出的伊扎克·丹齐格 (Yitzhak Danziger) 的《尼姆罗德》(Nimrod) 新照片引发了法律和道德争议，引发了一个问题：一件艺术品真正属于谁？</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 12:04:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-the-symbol-of-the-new-jew-ended-up-in-a-box-and-in-a-legal-dispute/00000191-2bd0-d2a9-a5dd-3fd966b60000</guid></item><item><title>美国驻日本大使因未邀请以色列而缺席长崎原子弹追悼会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/u-s-ambassador-to-japan-to-skip-a-bomb-memorial-service-because-israel-was-not-invited/00000191-2c62-d7d8-a7bb-ee7a3c1a0000</link><description>该市市长表示，鉴于国际社会对战争的反应，人们担心仪式上会出现抗议、破坏或袭击。加拿大、法国、德国、意大利和英国也发函表达了对以色列被排除在外的共同担忧</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:55:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/u-s-ambassador-to-japan-to-skip-a-bomb-memorial-service-because-israel-was-not-invited/00000191-2c62-d7d8-a7bb-ee7a3c1a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方突击搜查外交部，怀疑在发放外交护照方面存在不法行为——包括向内塔尼亚胡的儿子发放外交护照</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/police-raid-foreign-ministry-on-suspicion-of-illegally-granting-diplomatic-passports/00000191-2c19-d32b-ad9f-3d3b58c50000</link><description>据两名官员称，正在调查的其中一本护照是给总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的儿子亚伊尔·内塔尼亚胡的护照</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 09:20:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/police-raid-foreign-ministry-on-suspicion-of-illegally-granting-diplomatic-passports/00000191-2c19-d32b-ad9f-3d3b58c50000</guid></item><item><title>海法居民担心真主党的罢工将针对该市的危险材料港口区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/haifa-residents-fear-hezbollah-strike-will-target-citys-hazardous-materials-port-area/00000191-2bc2-d1b4-a399-7fe6b2ce0000</link><description>在真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉提到海法是火箭袭击的潜在目标后，尽管以色列军队下令减少石化产品库存，但其居民仍担心会发生危险材料事件</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 08:59:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/haifa-residents-fear-hezbollah-strike-will-target-citys-hazardous-materials-port-area/00000191-2bc2-d1b4-a399-7fe6b2ce0000</guid></item><item><title>AIPAC 的另一场胜利：韦斯利·贝尔 (Wesley Bell) 和 850 万美元击败“小队”成员科里·布什 (Cori Bush)</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/another-victory-for-aipac-wesley-bell-and-8-5-million-defeat-squad-member-cori-bush/00000191-2adb-d2a9-a5dd-3edb30180001</link><description>亲以色列游说团体的联合民主项目称赞这一结果“进一步证明亲以色列是两党的好政策和好政治”</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:29:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/another-victory-for-aipac-wesley-bell-and-8-5-million-defeat-squad-member-cori-bush/00000191-2adb-d2a9-a5dd-3edb30180001</guid></item></channel></rss>